1. *Bolje* je da se ne upuštamo u tu avanturu. (It is better not to get into this adventure.)
2. Ona se *bolje* oseća kad radi stvari za druge. (She feels better when she does things for others.)
3. *Bolje* je reći manje nego više. (It is better to say less than more.)
4. *Bolje* je da se pre nego što počnemo, sagledamo sve mogućnosti. (It is better to take a look at all the possibilities before we start.)
5. On je *bolje* razumeo situaciju nego mi. (He understood the situation better than us.)
6. *Bolje* je da se ne odupiremo promenama. (It is better not to resist the changes.)